    "summary": "ConfigCat exposes two authenticated HTTP APIs (the Public Management API and a SCIM User Provisioning API), plus an authenticated `configcat` CLI and a local stdio MCP server package `@configcat/mcp-server` that uses Public Management API credentials.",
