        "label": "Public Management API basic-auth credentials",
        "generateUrl": "https://app.configcat.com/my-account/public-api-credentials",
        "setup": "In the ConfigCat app, open [Public API credentials](https://app.configcat.com/my-account/public-api-credentials) and create Public Management API credentials. ConfigCat issues a basic-auth username and password; send them in the `Authorization: Basic ...` header or supply them to supported tools as `CONFIGCAT_API_USER` and `CONFIGCAT_API_PASS`."
      },
